sourcesContent: function e(e){var t=e.isItemSelectable,r=e.visualFocusItemIndex,i=e.itemsCount;if(i-1>=r)for(var n=1;i>=n;n++){var u=(r+n)%i;if(t(u))return u}}function t(e){for(var t=e.isItemSelectable,r=e.visualFocusItemIndex,i=e.itemsCount,n=1;i-1>=n;n++){var u=r-n;if(0>u&&(u=i+u),t(u))return u}}export{e as getNextSelectableIndex,t as getPreviousSelectableIndex};
